--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com, &quot;judy_in_hollywood&quot; &lt;Ticket_to_Heaven@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt; Hi All,  I was listening, with my ear-cups type headphones that were plugged into the RS Hack 469, for maybe 30 mins., not tapping (ran out of tape), and in the forground could hear voice/words every now and then (EVP&#39;s?), but . . . . in the background -throughout!- I could hear (but barely make out) a person -male- talking like from an interview! I had asked if anyone was here with a message, or if Mike & Lisa was there, or if John Lennon would like to say something (was it him??), then listened!  Has any of you experienced this???  =Judy=
&gt;
  P.S. This effect, I got, is like doing the sweep/scan and not only hearing voices/words (popping up) but also like someone&#39;s talking in the background thru-out the sweep/scan!!!   Anyone have this happen to them?  =Judy=
